anscombe_long <- data.frame(x = c(x1, x2, x3, x4), 
                            y = c(y1, y2, y3, y4), 
                            group = a_levels)

ggplot() R 

theme_set(theme_bw())
ggplot(data = anscombe_long, mapping = aes(x = x,y = y)) +
  geom_point(size = 4) +
  geom_smooth(method = "lm", fill = NA, fullrange = TRUE) +
  facet_wrap(~ group)
